// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1087 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 1ba10199-f7aa-5d0a-a6e5-4235a0bd4889

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:10* OR ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:9*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
